    public class setReplyTo_Test
extends MailTest
    This class tests the setReplyTo() API. It does this by passing various valid input values and then checking the type of the returned object.

    Set the addresses to which replies should be directed.

    api2test: public void setReplyTo(Address[])

    how2test: Call this API with address arguments, then call getReply, if this operation is successfull then the testcase passes, otherwise it fails.
